title: [1508521049] Best Italian Restaurant: Casamia Coach challenge - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title. 

Gordon passes his judgement on italian restaurant, Casamia as he over sees their first challenge of trying to serve 30 customers ordering at the same time.
